{
  "$doc": "VibeFlow config. Roles are fixed; tools are configurable: active_profile picks which tool/model plays each role. Switch with `vibe profile set <name>` or the UI (`vibe ui`). Claude Code reads .claude/agents/*.md frontmatter for subagent models — keep them consistent. allow_auto_merge is ignored and always treated as false. Legacy flat `agents` key from older configs is still honored when no profiles/active_profile are present.",
